Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:35.03,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270\blur9\pos(1851,546)}只是這樣能夠被原諒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:38.49,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270\blur9\pos(1851,546)}鐺鐺地響起了聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:41.95,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270\blur9\pos(1851,546)}從心底溢了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:47.25,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270\blur9\pos(1851,546)}想像被世界漸漸敲響
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:51.75,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270\blur9\pos(1851,546)}吶吶、告訴我古怪未來的你
