Comment: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,————————Text-PartA————————
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.16,0:01:38.91,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:41.16,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙要讓人等到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:44.41,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,到底幹什麼才能那麼花時間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.04,0:01:46.79,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:49.63,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,從那傢伙出去已經過去多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.04,0:01:50.88,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,三天！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:52.71,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,已經無話可說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.96,0:01:54.84,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙到底有多蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.42,0:01:59.64,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,再說那傢伙應該也是被村民排斥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:03.56,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,慢吞吞如果再出了什麼事…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.60,0:02:04.60,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,別生氣別生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:09.19,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽要穿的…婚紗來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:13.07,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是找那個花了很多時間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:15.28,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.61,0:02:17.36,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是這樣也沒辦法了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:20.95,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,但是就算是這樣也太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:25.54,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,他的壽命也沒有長到可以這樣揮霍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:33.34,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  爸爸不是說會一起來  永遠在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:36.01,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽不幸福嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:39.22,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,當然幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.43,0:02:41.80,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,那就再稍微等一會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:50.02,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來  時間靜止的世界嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:53.06,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,在那裡會是什麼感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:54.90,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣？媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.23,0:02:57.53,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:09.25,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,這種地方竟然有房子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:13.29,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的距離為什麼到現在都沒人發現
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:16.25,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(930,990)}TSUKIHIKO
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:16.25,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是擄走少年兵的怪物的腹地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:22.51,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,但是少年兵那傢伙說怪物是自己的妻子…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.59,0:03:25.35,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物是少年兵的妻子？怎麼可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:29.93,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是怪物用妖術操縱了少年兵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:34.56,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,想要通過操縱少年兵  有朝一日襲擊村子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:37.02,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,如果變成那樣只能夠處理掉少年兵了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:40.28,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  你們聽好  趁早做完
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:43.87,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,真…真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:46.62,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,你磨蹭個什麼  走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:52.29,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.29,0:03:55.13,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼…剛才好像有腳步聲…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:57.00,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸回來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:03:59.34,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,少年兵嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:03.80,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(813,990)}SHION
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:03.80,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑  別過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:08.72,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,幹掉了嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.02,0:04:11.43,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  果斷一發解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:13.90,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽  媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:16.81,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  這是怪物的女兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:18.65,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}媽媽…！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:19.57,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,那頭髮  肯定沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:21.69,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  把這傢伙也幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:25.36,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…喂  她還很小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:26.95,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎麼說也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:28.83,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,拖拖拉拉的搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:30.95,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  讓我來…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:32.62,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,目隱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:35.25,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？！消失了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:37.59,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說…妖術？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:38.71,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,目覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:44.68,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:46.22,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:49.47,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,目欺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:55.19,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,目奪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:05:00.48,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,目合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:11.58,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,東躲西藏也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:13.79,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,縱使逃至天涯海角
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:16.21,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,爾等所在之處也立可知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:18.79,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,少年兵怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:19.88,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,快說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:25.38,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,不願直言則讀透汝心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:27.59,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,目竊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:33.85,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  快說怪物在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:38.40,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,不然…我們也不想打你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:42.19,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,不過…也不能放任來歷不明的東西！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:46.61,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(741,990)}AZAMI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:46.61,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,薊…薊是我的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:49.07,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,不准…出手！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:52.58,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  為什麼要包庇那個怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:54.25,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,你是人類吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:58.04,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,還要反抗的話…不會輕饒你！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:06:00.13,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,不是包庇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:02.63,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,不是全部說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:07.97,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和她…和家人永遠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:09.47,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:10.05,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:14.72,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！似乎發現信號一類的東西了  一直延續到森林那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:16.02,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:20.61,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,是少年兵為回去而準備的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:22.94,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,立即為退治怪物做準備！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.57,0:06:26.44,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多給我清醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:29.36,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,把她解決掉後  你也會清醒的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:31.20,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  快點做準備
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:32.70,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:37.62,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底對我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:38.91,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,滾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:41.08,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,給我滾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:44.13,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,然後永遠不許帶任何人來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:47.72,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了就趕快給我滾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:53.14,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,少年兵…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:08.94,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:11.53,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑  別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:14.62,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,別再靠近我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:18.50,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想再因我而讓你們受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:20.62,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:22.29,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是太笨了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.63,0:07:24.67,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,想要逃避世間之理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:27.84,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,並且還把你們也牽連進來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:31.80,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,其實已經意識到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:34.80,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有我在就不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:41.52,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,只要沒有我  你們就能在這個世界上幸福地生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:44.90,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我沒有祈盼幸福…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.73,0:07:48.82,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,只是稍微做了一會夢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:52.53,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,能永遠和家人生活在一起的幻想…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:55.20,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,太美好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:07:57.70,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,你們真是無可救藥得美好…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:07:59.75,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽！不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:04.25,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑  你不是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:06.63,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不要使用這種力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:09.88,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我沒有這樣說的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:14.93,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,但你要作為一個人類  和父親一起幸福地生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:18.35,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我的…幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:21.02,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！媽媽別走！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:26.40,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  對不起  對不起  對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:28.57,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠愛你們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:34.57,Default-2,NTP,0,0,0,,我會永遠祈禱你們能幸福  永遠…
Comment: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,————————Text-PartB————————
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.37,0:09:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉這樣不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又想要擅自出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面好像很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  別說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我給你讀連環畫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是哦  可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:45.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到這裡一起讀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那今天就讀這個故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那天開始  從媽媽留下我們消失那天開始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底過了多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸去世的時候  茉莉呱呱墜地的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽都沒有回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽現在也在那個沒有終結的世界一個人生活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:22.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我的任性
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我一人等待著不知會不會歸來的媽媽也好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:38.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等茉莉再大些  就讓她見見外面的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.86,0:10:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個世界肯定會接受她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像媽媽對我所說的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在對我來說茉莉的幸福就是我的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好  不知道什麼時候睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:10:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:17.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉！在就應答我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？喂  怪物不是說只有一隻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別老想著以前的傳說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過也靠它找到了有意思的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊  這頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.34,0:11:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到時候做成展示品的話肯定能大賺一筆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛  住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:45.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們幾個  放開那孩子！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？區區個怪物說點什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:51.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老實點！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:12:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  要把他也一起抓了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.69,0:12:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你在聽我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.07,0:12:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  媽媽  我們…沒有變得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:47.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到  連她們也拉進這邊了  您真是壞心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個永不結束的世界的痛苦您不是最清楚的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:12:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:01.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  不會閉嘴的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.21,0:13:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順從於利己又輕鬆的欲望  創造出這個世界的不正是大人您嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來您的願望是把最愛的家人一起帶到這裡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是很好嘛  女兒和孫女一起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,願望終於實現了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說了閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起  真是愚蠢  沒錯  沒錯  就要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這才是我們的最大的快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.87,0:13:42.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑  這都是我的錯  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  就是這個表情  太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  對  就是這樣  變成這種悲劇全都是因為您
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少  至少只有這孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己丟掉了女王蛇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被那個附身的話  確實能救那孩子一命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:21.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  這樣也就沒有抑制這個世界的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,附身於您的蛇失去了女王是多麼的混亂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.97,0:14:36.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請放心吧  至少不會寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您對這世界所下達的把8月15日逝去的生命捲進來這條命令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:46.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經是無法停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰來…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見  我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:04.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦  要是不離家出走就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:08.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且都是修哉不好  都是修哉欺負人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不聽使喚地…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  你和家人走散了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許我也和你一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅色的眼睛也是一個樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:34.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  不要再走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰…來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才是…女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都是一個人  好寂寞  一個人好寂寞啊  誰來…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:06.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別過來  不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到我眼睛的話就會變成石頭的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.36,0:16:19.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…我必須得是一個人  所以請回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:26.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼喚我的人就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.53,0:16:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的  我和你是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:03.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都被別人忌諱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.87,0:17:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全用不著害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…那個…做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:18.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:27.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  我睡著了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:38.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  他去哪裡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都太過分了  把我丟下一起走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:18:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  有人在睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:03.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事嗎  會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口…口渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:12.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給  請喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不燙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸  嗯  不燙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害  你是從哪來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:33.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會在那裡睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼呢  不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  記性不怎麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.07,0:19:43.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記性不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也經常忘記東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然覺得要是能都記得就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:53.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不可思議呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.29,0:19:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一個  我還記得
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:20:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼什麼  是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要朋友  想和朋友一起玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.18,0:20:10.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋…友？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  但是我只記得這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想和朋友一起玩耍  只有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.94,0:20:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就和我做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.07,0:20:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:29.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:35.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以介紹我的朋友給你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:40.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…大家一定很樂意…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都已經深夜0時了  還有如此人群
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.13,0:20:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難以置信  到底發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小桃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.14,0:20:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如您所見  非常的吵鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:20:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的  能聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.52,0:20:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上是從現場發來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:06.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也去吧  大家一定都在那裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:10.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的朋友
Comment: 0,0:22:40.96,0:22:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,————————Text-PartC————————
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.50,0:22:46.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少女失去了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.76,0:22:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的重要的朋友  全都不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.10,0:22:56.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少女一個人哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.06,0:23:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想再一次和大家一起玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.15,0:23:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少女無數次如此祈願
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.11,0:23:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼向少女搭話了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.45,0:23:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實現您的願望吧  實現您的渴望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為您帶來一個能實現您的空想的世界吧
